caption;Versi 2
no;1
p;God sent His son, they called Him Jesus
p;He came to love, heal, and forgive.
p;He lived and died to buy my pardon,
p;An empty grave is there to prove my Savior lives.
empty
no;ref
pi;Because He lives, I can face tomorrow.
pi;Because He lives, All fear is gone.
pi;Because I know He holds the future,
pi;And life is worth the living just because He lives.
